Package net.regsirius06.engine.labyrinth

Class Labyrinth2D

java.lang.Object
net.regsirius06.engine.labyrinth.Labyrinth2D
All Implemented Interfaces:
Iterable<List<WallType>>
public class Labyrinth2D extends Object implements Iterable<List<WallType>>
Represents a 2D labyrinth with walls and light sources. This class provides functionality for managing and interacting with the labyrinth, including generation, access to wall types, collision detection, and managing light sources.
